{
  "stem": "27748.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And really, for the next eight years or so, I had-- I had employment of a very minimal sort, working for a foundation here in Baltimore.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was earning virtually no income.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a period where my marriage dissolved.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a breakdown.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was hospitalized for three weeks for depression.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My-- my marriage ended and I was earning virtually no income.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the whole world dissolved in many ways for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there was one thing that didn't end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In fact, it began during about that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I started to address myself to the Holocaust professionally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then a little later, I started to address myself to it personally.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The professional thing was I felt that a good deal of the writings about the Holocaust was not daring enough intellectually, that we were-- that we were assuming that only monsters do monstrous things.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was starting from the notion that very ordinary people can do monstrous things, but the trick is to explain how this can work, people like ourselves, whereas the party line among survivors, among scholars was the Germans were totally different from the rest of us.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Even now we have writings that say their particular brand of anti-Semitism is so unique, nobody else's is like that, or it is the uniqueness of the issue of anti-Semitism that's bad.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I'm saying it is in the character of human beings, ordinary human beings, to use their makeup, the same makeup for good and for evil, can be used for good or for evil, and we can discover how it works.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I felt an intellectual challenge that I felt wasn't being met.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I started to publish articles in 1982.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I kept writing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
